Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(800,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:01:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Secret of the Hieratic Text"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's the\N Winged Sun Dragon of Ra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's{\i0} the Winged Sun Dragon of Ra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get that it's round like the sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is that {\i1}all{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This don't look a thing like what appeared in my Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I feel it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel its overwhelming presence!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it shines with a divine light radiant of God!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm certain this is authentic!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:02:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The three Harpy Ladies I sacrificed should have met the Summoning Conditions...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So... How did {\b0}this{\b1} happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you Summoned is the true Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Winged Sun Dragon of Ra...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's its true form?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a pity...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for a Duelist of {\i1}your{\i0} caliber to control a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Duelists chosen\N by God can {\i1}wield{\i0} a god!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a card falls\N into the hands of a Duelist,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all its powers belong to the Duelist who possesses it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of now, the God Card is {\i1}mine{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, take a look at the God Card set on your Duel Disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the text space of the card...\N Some kind of hieroglyphics?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I took the card from Malik,\N there was nothing written in the text space!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now there's definitely hieroglyphs written there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you decipher the script?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It contains the {\i1}key{\i0} to awakening the true powers of Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ra's true powers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ra has quite the {\i1}terrifying{\i0} Special Abilities hidden within it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hidden Special Abilities within Ra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! I can't see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the card look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba, use the "Satellite Search" to capture the image of it set on Mai Kujaku's Duel Disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then scan the God Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start on it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What secrets lie in Ra's card text?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way I can translate this text's meaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you can read that text, you can't control Ra or activate its Special Abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll tell you one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those letters are Hieratic Text!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ancient letters written by the priests.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hieratic Text...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ancient letters written by the priests?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a language used for law, literature and religion in Ancient Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike the common {\i1}demotic{\i0} text, only those with special status were taught it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}chosen ones{\i0} can\N read it with their {\i1}hearts{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's only natural we Tomb Guardians know it as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A card existing in a card game that only "special people" can use?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the {\i1}creator{\i0} of Duel Monsters, Pegasus J. Crawford,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,couldn't decipher the\N hidden abilities of Ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was forced to literally transcribe the Hieratic Text right onto the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it holds a special feature that makes the letters only become visible in the light emitted by Ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He let me steal his God Card on purpose, knowing I can't use it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Ra is in Sphere Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It acts as a motionless ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now try solving the riddle to change it to Battle Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and take control of the god, Mai Kujaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Malik! Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was never afraid of losing Ra from the start?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik {\i0\b0}wanted{\i1\b1} Mai to Summon Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai Kujaku sacrificed three Harpy ladies to Summon the God...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ra's Attack and Defense Power is determined by the total points of the Monsters used to Summon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other words, Ra should have 5400 Attack and 4200 Defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And yet the god remains silent...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not showing any signs of attacking or defending...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What does the text say?\N What is the condition to activate Ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is there any way to use it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As far as you are concerned, that god may as well not {\i1}exist{\i0} on your field.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:06:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I attack you with one of my Monsters next turn, the god won't protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you decipher the secret of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will suffer that\N hellish pain once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could always {\i1}pray to God{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My face-down Trap is Gravity Bind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I activate it, all 4 Star Monsters are forbidden to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the meantime, I'll work on trying to decipher Ra's secrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Holding Legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pity you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing has a Special Ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this card is played on the board,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all reverse cards are sent back to the player's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, when the two cards Holding Arms and Holding Legs are gathered together...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Sacred Palette\N of Wadjet is called forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither Magic nor Traps nor God can protect you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the darkness and pain embrace you, Mai Kujaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding Arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding Legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This should only be Solid Vision...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't {\i1}move{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I {\i1}told you{\i0}\N that this is a {\i1}Dark Game{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything that happens here is {\i1}real{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the {\i1}pain{\i0} you feel from the attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Directly attack the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... hear it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That warm voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Give yourself to the pain!\N -Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite an entertaining show, isn't it Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall now begin the preparations for the Sacrifice of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sacrifice of Darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen {\i1}very closely{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ra has three Special Abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll reveal just {\i1}one{\i0} of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Three Special Abilities?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?! He's chanting some kind of spell...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, take a look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ra's changing its form!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This must be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of Ra's abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}God himself{\i0} will serve the player who utters the sacred text!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awaken, Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My{\i0} turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With one attack from Ra, I'll burn this woman up with Ra's sacred flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On this turn, Ra's attack will reduce Mai's Life to nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If this is a Dark Game, the moment Mai loses...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a perfect sacrifice, Mai Kujaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Restrained as you are, unable to move your arms and legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even place your hand on your deck to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it quick,\N just one attack from Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become ash and spread into darkness!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him...! If he doesn't stop, Mai will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This match is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to attack her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your eyes open, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will sacrifice this woman to the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And draw out all\N your hatred in the process!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On my back is\N carved the Seal of Memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It tells the location of the Pharaoh's memories that my family has protected for thousands of years!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All so that one day, it can be presented to the resurrected soul of the Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Seal of Memories...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that purpose and that purpose alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,countless generations of my family lived and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only birthright was darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a deep scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despair and pain. That is all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the trauma that dominates my other self!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness robbed him of his freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even more darkness was born in his self-pitying heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the {\i1}pain{\i0} and {\i1}hatred{\i0} that exists within his dark heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things belong to {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's Malik's split personality!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My birthday was when he was ten years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the day the Rite of the Tomb Guardians was performed on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His father filled him\N with pain and sadness...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until his heart was so enshrouded that all he wanted to do was die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So in order to survive,\N in order to keep {\i1}living{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he had to create another self.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the moment I was born, I always knew I would take his personality over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there was one thing which stood in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only switch personalities when he is filled with rage...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rishid...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without even knowing, that man sealed me away within the carving on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And sealed {\i1}his{\i0} anger along with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was confined deep inside Malik's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the moment he fell unconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am {\i1}finally{\i0} the {\i1}ruler{\i0} of this body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you {\i1}want{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The God Cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I {\i1}want{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}have{\i0} no needs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you really want an {\i1}answer{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get rid of all light and order...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I want to {\i1}destroy{\i0} all lives aside from my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Destruction{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destruction is my {\i1}pleasure{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what gives birth to my {\i1}world{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world of {\i1}darkness and death{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will send this woman to perish in the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before he attacks Mai with Ra...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lower the Duel Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! This Duel is not over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be disqualified, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ra! Burn that woman!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winged Sun Dragon of Ra! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}!!\N-Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, get out of here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That woman won't remember you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear something in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A warm voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really... don't know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}me{\i0}, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jou...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we friends who've fought together all this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're... friends...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta win so you can Duel against me and Yugi, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let you forget all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you a huge debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was struck by lightning and fell unconscious in my Duel earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream about everyone that helped save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason I didn't have the strength to stand up,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then you guys all reached out your hands to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And {\i1}you{\i0} were there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was {\i1}embarrassing{\i0},\N so I didn't tell you before!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, you were {\i1}there{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jou...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai! So you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So their bond actually broke the Power of Darkness...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is {\i1}my{\i0} fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Isn't this Solid Vision?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't it budge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're always by my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbass! You think I can do that {\i1}now{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Blaze Cannon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got another fight waiting for you! Come on!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I can stand and watch my friend get killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you, Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The reason I entered this tournament was so that I could see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yugi!\N -Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It almost makes my {\i1}cry{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throwing yourself in front of Ra's attack to prevent your pals from dieing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik...! Your anger and hatred...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it all on my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I swear to send\N you back to the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yugi!\N -Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk while you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon I'll crush you into pieces along with the Millennium Puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And scatter them into\N the darkness for all eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yugi!\N -Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Pull yourself together, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Ra's attack just now, the woman lost all her Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's game over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey judge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call my name and\N announce me the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And {\i1}loudly{\i0} if you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tournament third round!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner is Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik {\i1}Ishta{\i0}r. The {\i1}real one{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I tear him apart\N right here and now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I merely {\i1}jest{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy Yugi in a {\i1}Duel{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a match most befitting those chosen by the Millennium Items... in the ultimate Dark Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't move...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can kill {\i1}you{\i0} whenever I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:18:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, it's about time you give me my God Card back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky you got away with your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll wish you had\N died here {\i1}painlessly{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The loser of a Dark Game\N must be {\i1}punished{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punished...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai Kujaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I plan on letting you enjoy the inside of the world in your mind to the {\i1}fullest{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are inside a space that exists deep within your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't {\i1}they{\i0} seem to be having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you will {\i1}never{\i0}\N get to return to them {\i1}again{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this Ra card is pulled out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the sand of memory will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when it does,\N your entire memory will disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you'll be slowly tortured to death as you perish in the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be slow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh so {\i1}slow{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll feel the pain of losing one friend after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, good night...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking my card back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik, what the hell did you do to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we speak, that woman is falling deeper and deeper into darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She shall suffer both extreme loneliness and suffering in her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman won't remember a {\i1}thing{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither you nor Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Where was I born?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Where did I live?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she'll forget the very {\i1}reason{\i0} she exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:20:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll wander in immeasurable loneliness, doomed to never regain conscious again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you {\i1}defeat{\i0} me, there's a {\i1}chance{\i0} she'll recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much are you\N going to hurt my friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll {\i1}kill{\i0} you, Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kick your sorry ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax. I'll drown {\i1}you{\i0}\N in darkness soon as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The power inside\N me has been released...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The more souls I sacrifice to the darkness, the more it fuels my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! She's still unconscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't beat Malik, Mai will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait for me, Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I promise I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Yugi's awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, don't overdo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alright...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}, what about {\i1}Mai{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik did this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The hidden personality born from Malik's subconscious...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, please don't hurt yourself anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Mokuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, the text on the Ra card has been successfully scanned!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll analyze it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm proceeding to the fourth round of the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear the loser off of my field!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's now time for my god, Obelisk, to descend!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to become a sacred arena!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(136,141)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} is still unconscious and not waking up, the fourth match begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s opponent is the eighth Duelist whom no one has seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the person we met in the Ancient Egyptian exhibit at the museum, Ishizu-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are {\i1}you{\i0} doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing the future\N with her Millennium Tauk,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishizu-{\i1}san{\i0} declares Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:22:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do feel bad for Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kaiba VS the Eighth Duelist"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.96,0:22:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.89,0:22:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.14,0:23:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
